description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for dynamic and motivated individuals to join Warwickshire ICT Services as ICT Desktop Engineers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of an energetic, experienced and innovative support team constantly developing and implementing existing and new technology. You will be directly involved in our efforts to provide the best ICT services across the NHS in Warwickshire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Technical Services Manager you will ensure SLA&#39;s are proactively delivered and services maintained to the highest possible standards. The scope &amp; volume of work requires proven technical skills and a highly organised approach to operational delivery of end point devices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to be forward looking and have excellent interpersonal and communication skills, a calm positive attitude along with good organisational and high-quality customer service skills. It is important that the post holder can multi-task and work under pressure as well as deal with any emergency situations which may arise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking Desktop Engineers to work as part of the:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mobile Device Team&lt;/strong&gt; - supporting iPad and mobile phone deployment, maintenance and supporting staff across Warwickshire – Office based.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support Team&lt;/strong&gt; - triaging and supporting incidents and service requests. Working closely with the Service Desk Team and Senior Triage Team – Office based&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Service Delivery Team&lt;/strong&gt; – providing desktop support to staff based in sites across Warwickshire – Field based&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held via MS Teams during week commencing 16th November&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Avinder Channa - Technical Services Manager - avinder.channa@swft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ravi Heer – Technical Services Manager – ravi.heer@swft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eric MacFarlane – Technical Services Manager – eric.macfarlane@swft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mike Bidwell – Technical Services Manager – Michael.bidwell@swft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
